  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduo a Librep</title>

    <para>
      The <application>librep</application> package contains a Lisp system.  This
is useful for scripting or for applications that may use the Lisp
interpreter as an extension language.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

